    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel supply tomorrow through National Fuel Admit Card",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said that the National Fuel Licensing System has been successfully tested at two locations in Colombo.",
        "Kanjana Wijesekara said that fuel will be provided under this fuel permit system at selected fuel filling stations covering all the districts of the country tomorrow.",
        "Meanwhile, Power Minister Kanjana Wijesekara said that another ship containing petroleum has arrived in the country and after its samples have been tested, distribution activities will be carried out. (a)"
      ],
